title: 3 Br 2 bath in south Minneapolis minutes to DT close to everything
posting_body: ['This large upper Unit with an open concept has A/C, freshly painted, near a bus stop, and is minutes to DT.', 'Rent is $ 1600.00; included in the rent is water & trash.', 'Available Now.', 'For showing please text', 'show contact info', 'or email full names and date of birth of all adults planning to live in the unity for pre-screening', 'Application Fee: $35 per adult', 'The $35 application fee per adult will be used to conduct a background check that encompasses the following four areas:', '(1) Criminal history', '(2) Employment/Wage verification', '(3) Prior rental history', 'Requirements:', 'Clean criminal record per city guideline .', 'Good standing rental history, no evictions and/or unlawful detainers for the past 3 years.', 'Verifiable monthly income, 2.5 times the rent amount.', 'In order to secure the rental property the approved applicant is required to place a deposit', 'All approved tenants are required to sign up for Service Plus with Centerpoint Energy or HomeSmart with Xcel Energy upon approval']
